	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />When used in-game, Battletoads' PCM sound effects even break parallax effects, presumably because they steal all of the CPU's attention.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


	<hr width="85%" />

	<table width="85%" cellspacing="3" cellpadding="0" border="0" align="center">
