	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />The other thing Battletoads does is drop out the PCM drums entirely for parts of the intro so that it can manage more animation.<br /><br />Big Bird's Hide and Speak cuts many of its samples into separate segments to slip little animation updates in between them (mostly Big Bird's mouth), which I thought was interesting.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


