		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Add Karate Champ to the list.  Be-gin!<br /><br />This isn't associated with a game, but back around 2004 I made my Squeedo synth cartridge.  It's audio was generated by an MCU on cart, but was played through $4011.  I guess it is still the only expansion audio cart for an unmodified NES?

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


